Package: bsv
Type: Package
Title: BSV - Base of Security Vectors
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Maksim", "Bovin", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "bovin@example.com"),
    person("Daria", "Kurilenko", role = "aut", email = "kurilenko@example.com"),
    person("Anastasia", "Timonina", role = "aut", email = "timonina@example.com"))
Description: Analytical toolkit for harvesting cybersecurity-related papers
    from arXiv, enriching them with MITRE ATT&CK techniques (via rules or LLM),
    storing results in PostgreSQL and exposing them through a plumber2 REST API
    that backs both a Shiny dashboard and an MCP server for AI agents.
